The Sector Commander, Federal Road Safety Corps, Lagos State Command, Olusegun Ogungbemide, on Wednesday, insisted that there are no demon, witch or wizard at Otedola Bridge. According to him, the frequent crashes recorded around the bridge is caused by reckless drivers who drive expired trucks. Ogungbemide spoke on Wednesday at the Quarterly Stakeholders’ Meeting of the Lagos State Emergency Management Agency held at the Lagos Chambers of Commerce and Industries. The Otedola Bridge is notorious for road crashes mostly involving fuel-laden tankers and trucks that often explode, resulting in inferno, burnt vehicles, loss of lives and properties. Details later…